flowchart TD
    A([Sales / Purchase / Expense event]) --> B[Build VoucherEntry list:<br/>account_id, debit, credit]
    B --> C[create_voucher voucher_type, entries, ref]
    C --> D{Sum debit == Sum credit ?}
    D -- No --> E[[Raise ValueError: unbalanced]]
    D -- Yes --> F[Persist Voucher + entries]
    F --> G[Generate voucher_number: VCH-XXXX]
    G --> H[Commit transaction]
    H --> I[Return Voucher object]
    I --> J([Reflected in Trial Balance + P&L reports])
